.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-3-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, soy-milk
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, marigold
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  dancer, teacher
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, western
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, ice-hockey
The people use 2 different means of transport: scooter, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the dancer##3
2. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
3. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person watching disaster movies##3
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |
| Beverage      | hot-chocolate | soy-milk  |
| Flower          | marigold   | begonia   |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | puzzles   |
| Job           | dancer        | teacher   |
| Movie-Genre   | western      | disaster |
| Sport         | ice-hockey    | climbing  |
| Transport     | scooter       | taxi      |

