3. the person drinking soy-milk is the vegafina-smoker##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who likes blue##1
5. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |
